Revenue per booking: ~\u8377?255\par
\par
If CampIn does 100 bookings/month \f4\u8594?\f2  \f0\u8377?25,500/month\par
If CampIn does 1,000 bookings/month \f4\u8594?\f2  \f0\u8377?2,55,000/month\par
