### 3.1 Instagram Launch Strategy\par
\par
Instagram is CampIn's **most important acquisition channel** in early stages. The influence of social media platforms such as Instagram, Facebook, Snapchat, Twitter, YouTube, and others influences the tech-savvy generation, primarily Gen-Z and millennials. The capturing and uploading of adventurous treks, camping experiences, and beautiful scenery on these social media platforms attracts the young urban population, pushing them to pursue such trips and adventures.\par
\par
**Content Pillars for @campin.india:**\par
\par
| Pillar | Content Type | Frequency |\par
|---|---|---|\par
| "Hidden India" | Beautiful spot reveals with camping context | 3x/week |\par
| Host Stories | Short reels of real host personalities | 1x/week |\par
| Road Trip Culture | Campervan/SUV camping reels | 2x/week |\par
| Community Moments | Campfire gatherings, sunrise camps | 2x/week |\par
| Tips & Education | Beginner camping guides, packing lists | 1x/week |\par
| Behind CampIn | Founder story, building in public | 1x/week |\par
