**Database Schema (Supabase):**\par
\par
```sql\par
-- USERS TABLE\par
users: id, name, email, phone, user_type (camper/host), \par
       verified, avatar_url, created_at\par
\par
-- LISTINGS TABLE\par
listings: id, host_id, title, location, lat, lng, \par
          description, type, price_per_night, \par
          washroom, electricity, water, parking, \par
          campervan_friendly, tent_allowed,\par
