# PART 9: TRUST & SAFETY ARCHITECTURE\par
\par
Trust is not a feature in India. It's the foundation. Without trust, no Indian user will book an unknown campsite from a stranger.\par
\par
## 9.1 Trust Stack (Build in this order)\par
\par
**Level 1 \emdash  Basic Trust (MVP)**\par
- CampIn's phone number visible on every page\par
- Founder story visible (people trust founders, not companies)\par
- WhatsApp contact available\par
- "We review every submission personally" messaging\par
\par
**Level 2 \emdash  Platform Trust (Month 6+)**\par
- Phone OTP verification for all users\par
- Host identity verification (Aadhaar-linked, optional initially)\par
- Review system with verified stays only (no fake reviews)\par
- Host response rate displayed\par
- Clear cancellation and refund policy\par
\par
**Level 3 \emdash  Community Trust (Month 12+)**\par
- CampIn Verified Host badge (rigorous manual check)\par
- Community moderation team\par
- Safety guidelines published\par
- Emergency contact information per listing\par
- Insurance partnership exploration\par
